{"tid":1677337,"cid":28,"subCid":0,"title":"行動post推唔上，唔洗靠熱門嫁，不如分好台等大家要揾都易d揾，易d推？","createTime":"2019-10-27T04:50:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-27T13:33:37.000Z","uid":20447,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c6af0464049a666a5a471a107facdbc1b8b475ef","tid":1677337,"uid":20447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T04:50:51.000Z","msg":"利申：平時都係上熱門多<br />\n小弟日日上連登，但係d行動資訊仲少過家中媽媽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而家d資訊又多又亂，我地可以分台集中資訊，方便推文。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n例如:<br />\n未來活動-&gt;活動台<br />\n咁就可以方便到有心推同揾活動既連登仔<br />\n(Btw幾分鐘前活動台頭幾個post仲係90巴絲聚會之類)<br />\n<br />\n遊行當日-&gt;直播台<br />\n<br />\n新聞-&gt;時事台<br />\n<br />\n查案-&gt;講故台？<br />\n<br />\n我知有好多巴絲都有分台，但係我地要推廣等多d人有呢個習慣，亦都要教新會員唔好淨係睇熱門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後要多謝黃絲小姐成日whatsapp文宣比我媽媽，雖然我唔知你係邊個，但係你一定係個好女仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a88d4960ed9200dee579d136edf1eb857a8b89ec","tid":1677337,"uid":20447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T04:51:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"dc18c3552e91f8b4a754762d1424e41c60e66a64","tid":1677337,"uid":20447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T04:51:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4a395f23d09eaabfd2ea3eee41958ab1b17b1ac8","tid":1677337,"uid":321048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T04:52:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/U6eAr0n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FU6eAr0n.jpg&h=ef51d913&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f44b869c2a3150c57e3a089d74beec470f872a6d","tid":1677337,"uid":20447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T04:52:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4490791762